    {
      "parameters": {
        "jsCode": "const item = $input.first();\nconst sheetName = item.json.sheetName;\nconst rows = item.json.rows;\nconst dataStr = JSON.stringify(rows);\n\nconst instructions = {\n  demand_global: `Analyse the tab \"demand_global\".\\n- Compare current month volume vs M-1 (% and absolute number).\\n- Compare current month vs same month previous year (% and absolute number).\\n- Summarise the 1-year trend: is it globally increasing or decreasing vs previous year?\\nUse bullet points. English only. Real numbers only, no placeholders.`,\n  demand_transaction: `Analyse the tab \"demand_transaction\" (columns: date, segment.transaction, volume).\\n- Compare each segment current month vs M-1 (% and absolute).\\n- Compare each segment current month vs same month previous year (% and absolute).\\n- Which segments are increasing vs decreasing?\\nUse bullet points. English only. Real numbers only, no placeholders.`,\n  ranking_global_war: `Analyse the tab \"ranking_global_war\" (columns: date, url_hostname, rank_organic_war).\\n- What is Seloger Neuf current rank vs competitors?\\n- Has the rank improved or declined recently?\\nUse bullet points. English only. Real numbers only, no placeholders.`,\n  demand_asset: `Analyse the tab \"demand_asset\".\\n- Global demand trend month over month (% evolution).\\n- Per asset type: is demand increasing, stable or decreasing?\\nUse bullet points. English only. Real numbers only, no placeholders.`,\n  demand_departement: `Analyse the tab \"demand_departement\".\\n- Top 10 departments by volume for the last 3 months.\\n- For each: is volume increasing, stable or decreasing over the last 3 months?\\nUse bullet points. English only. Real numbers only, no placeholders.`,\n  audience: `Analyse the tab \"audience\".\\n- Compare nonbrand vs brand vs anonymous click share.\\n- Has the split changed recently?\\nUse bullet points. English only. Real numbers only, no placeholders.`\n};\n\nconst instruction = instructions[sheetName] || `Analyse the tab \"${sheetName}\". Provide key facts with real numbers. Use bullet points. English only.`;\n\nconst prompt = `You are a SEO and real estate analyst specialised in the French new residential market.\\n\\nYou receive real data from a digital performance tracking spreadsheet.\\n\\nSheet name: \"${sheetName}\"\\nNumber of rows: ${rows.length}\\nData:\\n${dataStr}\\n\\n${instruction}`;\n\nreturn [{ json: { ...item.json, prompt } }];\n"
      },
